---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="About Us - Square Root SEO | B2B Digital Growth Partner" description="Square Root SEO is a B2B-only digital marketing agency helping Indian manufacturers generate qualified leads from Google using the proprietary A.C.I.D Framework." activePage="about">

<!-- HERO -->
<section class="page-hero">
  <div class="container text-center">
    <span class="cmn-tag p1-bg">About Us</span>
    <h1>Built for <span class="p1-clr">B2B Manufacturers.</span> Only.</h1>
    <p class="page-hero__sub">We're a specialist digital marketing agency with one focus: helping Indian B2B manufacturers get qualified leads from Google.</p>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- OUR STORY -->
<section class="about-story">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="about-story__wrapper reveal">
      <div class="about-story__content">
        <span class="cmn-tag p3-bg" style="color:var(--n900-clr);">Our Story</span>
        <h2>Founded in December 2023. Built for Manufacturers.</h2>
        <p>Square Root SEO was founded in December 2023 with a clear mission: help B2B manufacturers stop depending on third-party marketplaces and start owning their digital presence. We saw that most SEO agencies offered generic packages that didn't work for industrial businesses. Manufacturers needed something built specifically for how their buyers search, evaluate, and buy.</p>
        <p>At Square Root SEO, our team's innovative approach to SEO project management has elevated brands to new heights. Harnessing the power of paid advertising, Google Ads, and AI, we've crafted compelling campaigns that resonate with audiences and drive qualified traffic using our proven A.C.I.D framework, built around Google's E-E-A-T principles.</p>
        <p>Today, we've built 50+ Digital Factories for manufacturers across packaging, chemicals, automation, textiles, and industrial supplies. Every strategy we deliver is backed by data, driven by AI, and measured by the leads it generates.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="about-story__highlights">
        <div class="about-story__highlight">
          <i class="fa-solid fa-calendar-check p1-clr"></i>
          <div>
            <h4>Founded</h4>
            <p>December 2023</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="about-story__highlight">
          <i class="fa-solid fa-building p3-clr"></i>
          <div>
            <h4>Headquarters</h4>
            <p>Indore, Madhya Pradesh</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="about-story__highlight">
          <i class="fa-solid fa-bullseye p2-clr"></i>
          <div>
            <h4>Specialisation</h4>
            <p>B2B Industrial SEO</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="about-story__highlight">
          <i class="fa-solid fa-robot p1-clr"></i>
          <div>
            <h4>Approach</h4>
            <p>AI-Powered + E-E-A-T Driven</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="about-usp">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-title text-center reveal">
      <span class="cmn-tag p1-bg">Why Choose Us</span>
      <h2>What Makes Square Root SEO Different</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="about-usp__grid reveal">
      <div class="about-usp__card">
        <div class="about-usp__icon" style="background:rgba(32,109,255,0.1);"><i class="fa-solid fa-industry p1-clr"></i></div>
        <h4>100% B2B Industrial Focus</h4>
        <p>We don't work with restaurants, salons, or e-commerce stores. Every client is a B2B manufacturer. That focus means we know your buyers, your keywords, and your sales cycle better than a generic agency.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="about-usp__card">
        <div class="about-usp__icon" style="background:rgba(255,181,37,0.1);"><i class="fa-solid fa-flask-vial p3-clr"></i></div>
        <h4>Proprietary A.C.I.D Framework</h4>
        <p>Not a checklist. A structured, 4-phase system (Architect, Content, Integration, Data) tested across 50+ manufacturing businesses. Repeatable. Measurable.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="about-usp__card">
        <div class="about-usp__icon" style="background:rgba(236,25,30,0.1);"><i class="fa-solid fa-chart-column p2-clr"></i></div>
        <h4>Data-Driven, Not Guesswork</h4>
        <p>Every keyword we target, every page we build, every piece of content is backed by real search data, competitor analysis, and buyer intent research. No vanity metrics, just leads.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="about-usp__card">
        <div class="about-usp__icon" style="background:rgba(12,12,14,0.05);"><i class="fa-solid fa-trophy n900-clr"></i></div>
        <h4>Proven Results, Not Promises</h4>
        <p>50+ Digital Factories built. 350% average traffic increase. ₹5+ Cr in B2B revenue generated. These are documented numbers from real manufacturing clients, not projections.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- MEET THE FOUNDER -->
<section class="about-founder">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="about-founder__wrapper reveal">
      <div class="about-founder__image">
        <img src="/punit-tongia.png" alt="Punit Tongia - Founder of Square Root SEO">
        <div class="about-founder__socials">
          <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/punittongia/" target="_blank" rel="noopener" title="LinkedIn"><i class="fa-brands fa-linkedin-in"></i></a>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="about-founder__content">
        <span class="cmn-tag p1-bg">Meet the Founder</span>
        <h2>Punit Tongia</h2>
        <p class="about-founder__title">Founder &amp; Certified SEO Expert</p>
        <p><a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/punittongia/" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="founder-link">Punit Tongia</a> founded Square Root SEO in December 2023 with a single conviction: Indian B2B manufacturers deserve a digital partner who actually understands their business. With deep expertise in SEO, Google Ads, and AI-driven digital strategy, Punit has personally architected the A.C.I.D Framework that powers every Digital Factory we build.</p>
        <p>His approach combines technical SEO precision with AI-powered content strategy, all grounded in Google's E-E-A-T principles. The result? Manufacturers who were invisible on Google are now ranking on page 1 and getting qualified buyer enquiries every week.</p>
        <div class="about-founder__badges">
          <div class="about-founder__badge">
            <i class="fa-solid fa-certificate p3-clr"></i>
            <span>Certified SEO Expert</span>
          </div>
          <div class="about-founder__badge">
            <i class="fa-solid fa-handshake p1-clr"></i>
            <span>Proud BNI Member</span>
          </div>
          <div class="about-founder__badge">
            <i class="fa-solid fa-robot p2-clr"></i>
            <span>AI-Driven Strategy</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- STATS BAR -->
<section class="stats-bar">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="stat-item reveal">
      <div class="stat-item__number" data-count="50" data-suffix="+">0</div>
      <div class="stat-item__label">Digital Factories Built</div>
    </div>
    <div class="stat-item reveal" style="transition-delay:0.1s;">
      <div class="stat-item__number" data-count="350" data-suffix="%">0</div>
      <div class="stat-item__label">Average Traffic Increase</div>
    </div>
    <div class="stat-item reveal" style="transition-delay:0.2s;">
      <div class="stat-item__number" data-count="5" data-prefix="₹" data-suffix="+ Cr">0</div>
      <div class="stat-item__label">B2B Revenue Generated</div>
    </div>
    <div class="stat-item reveal" style="transition-delay:0.3s;">
      <div class="stat-item__number" data-count="100" data-suffix="%">0</div>
      <div class="stat-item__label">B2B Industrial Focus</div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- CTA BANNER -->
<section class="page-cta reveal">
  <div class="container text-center">
    <h2>Ready to Work <span class="p3-clr">With Us?</span></h2>
    <p>We'll turn your website into a system that brings you B2B leads from Google.</p>
    <div style="display:flex; justify-content:center; gap:20px; flex-wrap:wrap; margin-top:30px;">
      <a href="/contact" class="common-btn p3-bg box-style">Contact Us <i class="fa-solid fa-arrow-right-long"></i></a>
      <a href="/acid-test" class="common-btn p1-bg box-style">Take Free ACID Test <i class="fa-solid fa-flask-vial"></i></a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

</BaseLayout>
